					<span class="label"><a href="">4.</a></span>
					<p>See Spencer W. Kimball, <span class="emphasis">The Teachings of Spencer W. Kimball,</span> ed. Edward L. Kimball (1982), 391.</p>
				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote5-10905_000_24nelson"><a name="5-10905_000_24nelson"> </a>
